{
  "text": "Input: G1 = (V1, E1), G2 = (V2, E2), v \u2208 V1 \u2229 V2, \u03b1, Output: q p \u21d0 SharpApproximatePR(v, \u03b1, ) [CITATION_1] for G1 q \u21d0 ApproxDirichPR(G2, V2 \\ V1, \u03b1, v, p, )",
